Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.61,0:18:49.19,Text-CH,,0,0,0,,9-tie
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.06,0:20:31.59,Text-CH,,0,0,0,,SELECTION PROJECT 第七赛季
