Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.06,0:21:03.49,Text-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.16,0:21:05.18,Text-CH,,0,0,0,,恭喜
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.64,0:21:06.98,Text-CH,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.55,Text-CH,,0,0,0,,好感动
